summary: I love how Eve is going to grow in skill at her job. It’s very important to me that she started out a mildly bad amateur who...
body:
I love how Eve is going to grow in skill at her job. It’s very important to me that she started out a mildly bad amateur who showed talent but had not had a formal chance to develop that talent. Now, she has that chance (Thanks, Villanelle, for the career) 

We get to see this journey of development and how her progress in her job working in espionage and desire to catch Villanelle is going to make her question her morality a lot more but be more successful the more she goes on. She’ll likely criticize Carolyn less for her loose morals and probably be criticized by Carolyn for perhaps going too far. But Eve’s going to conquer MI6 if it kills her
